models.gridobjects.items

Class Wall

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.gridobjects.GridObject
      • models.gridobjects.items.Item
        • models.gridobjects.items.Wall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Wall
extends Item
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Wall object extends Item and acts as a pure obstruction in the grid world. No EObject can interact with a Wall beyond being blocked by it.
    Author:
    Carmine Iannaccone
    See Also:
